"Who was it, a couple of minutes ago, that was telling me to 'throw the silly thing away'?"\par
Chet's sputtered reply was interrupted by Cap, who spoke directly to the Hardy brothers.\par
"How would you fellows like to combine some detective work with fossils?" he asked.\par
